    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;enchantment&nbsp;(compulsion)&nbsp;[mind-affecting];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;bard 5, psychic 6, sorcerer/wizard 6, spiritualist 6, summoner 5, unchained Summoner 6, witch 6;\n    \n    <strong>Subdomain</strong>&nbsp;Competition 6, Heroism 6;\n    \n    <strong>Bloodline</strong>&nbsp;Martyred 6;\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;touch<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;creature touched<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 min./level<br>\n      <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Will negates (harmless);&nbsp;\n      <strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>This spell functions like @Compendium[pf1.spells.vqfrp8t0c1lw1jna]{Heroism}<em>,</em> except the creature gains a +4 morale bonus on attack rolls, saves, and skill checks, immunity to fear effects, and temporary hit points equal to your caster level (maximum 20).</p>\n</div>\n",
